				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">All five channels are digital in the sense that they're generated by feeding bits to a <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital-to-analog_converter" class="postlink">DAC</a>. Four of the five produce waveforms that an analog synth is also capable of.</div>

